title: Getting current app is more painful than I had previously thought! Starting from…
message:
Getting current app is more painful than I had previously thought! Starting from some build in Lollipop 5.1, even ActivityManager#getRunningAppProcesses() won't work. Using UsageStatsManager class now, to get that information.

Going to upload this as beta and gain test feedback before pushing to production.
